      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING HOPKINS (2) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close second, 1.75 lengths from the winner Black Tiara (30.00) at this track. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Must come into calculations. ZIPPING GRYLLIS (3) boasts a strong record this journey with 14 wins and five minors from 24 tries. Below best last time at this track (21.02) in a Mix 1/2/3, finishing a 8 length fifth. Can hit the frame with the right run. MISS TESS (1) has been out of the placings last two but shapes well for this if she can recapture her solid win a few runs back, getting around this track over 365m in 20.67. Top win three back and can measure up again. NICKO JACK (4) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage one length away in third (20.85). Comes out of a solid form race last start. Likely to be in the finish again.",
